	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Aed. pl., uncertain date. See MRR 2.467. It is possible that he was a municipal, not a Roman, aedile (ILLRP 463; cf. Badian, Dial. Di Archeol. 4-5, no. 2-3, 1972, 379).\n" .
